{"tid":1658413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"痴撚線 中計黨咁樣帶風向","createTime":"2019-10-16T13:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T17:31:11.000Z","uid":227217,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2d29466f1e34bd56a487204584b2e050c047a9","tid":1658413,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"喂屌，血債又票償？傻撚咗啊？<br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解人哋敢肆無忌憚咁打柒我哋？因為打撚完之後<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇後果</span></span>啊！知你香港人犬儒啊！係咪仲要俾人睇死？<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布 政府已經冇招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658225</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰被襲 大家千其唔好亂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658221</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n保持憤怒，勇武休息，和理非 10 月 20 assemble!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔升級，唔降級，跟返之前程度玩到2046，睇下邊個gg？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1658331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1658331</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話美國會割蓆啦，眾議院係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全票通過</span>條bill，人哋<span style=\"color: red;\">理撚得你裝飾裝修定裝假狗</span>咩，總之反華、反共已經成為咗兩黨最大共識，學藍絲話齋，人哋都係為利益㗎咋嘛，唔係貪你「畫面夠靚」。香港人，反抗啊屌！"},{"pid":"3d4835c073f9b9bcf18bfbf9e58a02cbb710871b","tid":1658413,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1f8e2ac7c76565c81b38258e422992d7b2d288f2","tid":1658413,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:16:44.000Z","msg":"去集中營休息啦不如"},{"pid":"20543d7fa8f266f240181dbc9bfedb58fc447b3e","tid":1658413,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"唔係叫大家衝動，係該做的事就要做，唔好有無謂嘅束縛"},{"pid":"34bc70bfdea8ee207c4c4b50f9786a385924230d","tid":1658413,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:18:08.000Z","msg":"休息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e4421f017b403f530785aec23e15bb82d48b75","tid":1658413,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"蒙撚曬面,你搵比佢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好嬲？聽日要見到文宣砌成o既10.20, 你先對得住岑子杰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">同埋保持憤怒, 今個星期是文宣週 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">星期日是和理非主場, 過埋星期日反佢枱</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rVBZAa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rVBZAa.jpg&h=fafe8c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e57bb860e9876181a71b1fd4fdd860ea137b57e","tid":1658413,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n<br />\n無必要班美國政客難做<br />\n本身今日民調已經講左<br />\n裝修黨鐵同埋店舖都係最多人反對（講緊勇武黃絲裡面有1/4反對）<br />\n<br />\n無論形象定係民意<br />\n都無必要"},{"pid":"6b31a8ebdf3ecd279a4ed04d782e0bf71829f26b","tid":1658413,"uid":227217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"唔好忘記，和理非係勇武最強嘅後盾，落場如是，文宣如是，國際戰線都係！"},{"pid":"c73010747a1b9da9f0a